  "QuestText": {
    "QuestInfo": [
      {
        "Language": "JPN",
        "Name": "\u964D\u308A\u6CE8\u3050\u7206\u9C57\u306E\u77E2",
        "Client": "\u4E2D\u5805\u30CF\u30F3\u30BF\u30FC",
        "Description": "\u81EA\u5206\u3067\u3082\u307E\u3060\u3053\u306E\u76EE\u3067\u898B\u305F\u3082\u306E\u304C\r\n\u4FE1\u3058\u3089\u308C\u306D\u3047\u2026\u3002\u72E9\u308A\u3092\u3057\u3066\u305F\u3089\r\n\u6025\u306B\u7A7A\u304B\u3089\u7206\u5F3E\u307F\u305F\u3044\u306A\u3082\u306E\u304C\r\n\u964D\u3063\u3066\u304D\u3066\u3042\u305F\u308A\u4E00\u9762\u304C\u4E00\u6C17\u306B\r\n\u7126\u571F\u3068\u5316\u3057\u305F\u3088\u3002\u3042\u3093\u306A\u3084\u3064\u3092\r\n\u653E\u3063\u3066\u304A\u3051\u3070\u751F\u614B\u7CFB\u304C\u72C2\u3046\u305E\u3002\r\n\u8155\u306B\u81EA\u6162\u304C\u3042\u308B\u3084\u3064\u3001\u72E9\u731F\u983C\u3080\uFF01",
        "Target": "\u30D0\u30BC\u30EB\u30AE\u30A6\u30B9\uFF11\u982D\u306E\u72E9\u731F",
        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Death From Above",
        "Client": "Mid-tier Hunter",
        "Description": "I\u0027ve never seen anything like it!\r\nFrom the skies I heard a distant\r\nroar and then \u0022it\u0022 came. Like hell\r\nfalling from the heavens, fire rained\r\ndown, scorching the earth. Time\r\nalmost stood still as everything\r\naround me was consumed by flame.",
        "Target": "Hunt a Bazelgeuse",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "La mort venue du ciel",
        "Client": "Chasseur interm\u00E9diaire",
        "Description": "J\u0027ai jamais rien vu de pareil !\r\nJ\u0027ai entendu un rugissement dans\r\nle ciel, et c\u0027est l\u00E0 qu\u0027il est\r\narriv\u00E9. Une pluie infernale\r\nl\u0027accompagnait, an\u00E9antissant tout\r\nsur son passage, un spectacle\r\nhorrible \u00E0 figer le temps.",
        "Target": "Chasser un Bazelgeuse",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Morte dall\u0027alto",
        "Client": "Cacciatore mediano",
        "Description": "Non ho mai visto nulla del\r\ngenere! Ho sentito un ruggito\r\nlontano nel cielo e poi fiamme\r\ninfernali scese dall\u0027alto hanno\r\nflagellato la terra. Il tempo\r\npareva essersi fermato mentre\r\ntutt\u0027intorno veniva arso.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Bazelgeuse",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Tod von oben",
        "Client": "Mittelst\u00E4ndiger J\u00E4ger",
        "Description": "So was hab ich noch nie gesehen!\r\nVom Himmel t\u00F6nte ein ferner Schrei,\r\ndann kam \u0022er\u0022. Feuer regnete nieder\r\nund versengte die Erde, als fiele die\r\nH\u00F6lle vom Himmel. Die Zeit stand\r\npraktisch still, als alles um mich her\r\nvon Flammen verschlungen wurde.",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Bazelgeuse.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Lluvia mortal",
        "Client": "Cazador intermedio",
        "Description": "\u00A1Nunca he visto nada igual!\r\nEscuch\u00E9 un rugido en el cielo\r\ny, de la nada, lleg\u00F3 \u0022eso\u0022.\r\nEmpez\u00F3 a llover fuego que lo\r\nincendi\u00F3 absolutamente todo.\r\nMirase donde mirase, solo\r\npod\u00EDa ver llamas.",
        "Target": "Caza un Bazelgeuse",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0421\u043C\u0435\u0440\u0442\u044C \u0441 \u0432\u044B\u0441\u043E\u0442\u044B",
        "Client": "\u041E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u043D\u0438\u043A \u0441\u0440\u0435\u0434\u043D\u0435\u0433\u043E \u0443\u0440\u043E\u0432\u043D\u044F",
